**Preferences and Patterns Summary:**

- **DIY Beauty:** Strong inclination towards self-care products, particularly nail and eyebrow cosmetics. Purchases indicate a desire to recreate salon-quality results at home while minimizing costs.

- **Gel Nail Polish:** Repeated acquisition of gel nail polish sets suggests a significant interest in nail art, aesthetically appealing colors (such as glitter and neon), and versatility (matte and glossy finishes).

- **Value for Money:** Frequent mentions of avoiding salon expenses reflect a cost-conscious attitude, selecting products that offer good quality at affordable prices.

- **Cruelty-Free and Non-Toxic Products:** Multiple purchases feature brands that emphasize being cruelty-free and non-toxic, indicating a preference for ethical and safe beauty products.

- **Makeup Tools:** Investing in high-quality makeup brushes highlights an appreciation for effective application tools that are soft and versatile for various cosmetic needs.

- **Family-Oriented Choices:** Some purchases, such as temporary tattoos and hair products, indicate a focus on family-oriented activities or products catering to children, reflecting a balance between personal indulgence and family fun.

In conclusion, this individual values affordable, high-quality beauty and cosmetic products, particularly those that support DIY endeavors, ethical considerations, and family engagement.

features: DISPOSABLE TOWELS: Keep your hands clean and soft with our natural alternative to harsh chemical-based products. Our travel size wipes use quality essential oils to clean your hands without drying out your skin. Our refreshing and cleansing travel towels are so easy to use!

TRAVEL FRIENDLY: Our travel wipes are excellent companions for trips or long flights. They can be used on the bus, subway, or in public restrooms. These no-rinse shower wipes can help you refresh yourself when you're on the go. Our handy facial wipes are great for hot and humid days. Always stay fresh and ready to take on the day!

MULTIPURPOSE: Our facial cleansing wipes can also be used to cleanse your hands instead of using drying sprays. They are fantastic body wipes for women and men while they are traveling. They also make great camping wipes, a necessity if you will be in the wilderness for a while and still want to stay fresh and clean.

AROMATHERAPY TOWELETTES: Our handy wipes are perfect for every day use. With a variety of different scents, you can enhance your day to both energize the beginning of it or soothe yourself at the end.

CONVENIENT & PORTABLE: All of our body wipes are small and individually wrapped, ready to take on the go! Toss in your purse, suitcase, wallet, pocket, or backpack. These wipes are so much easier to carry around than a spray and work (almost) as well as a shower!
description: The Essential Oil Towelettes from Herban Essentials combines clean hands with soothing scents. Our travel hand wipes work to keep your hands clean and skin soft. They also work as face cleansing wipes, face cloths, body wipes for adults bathing, and body wipes for men when you are traveling and cannot stop to take a shower. If you need a midday refresher, use one of our citrus moisture towelettes for an energizing pick-me-up! Our collection includes lemon wipes, facial wipes cleansing cloths, a natural towelette, and men's wipes.
